title: YU-GI-OH! Yugioh TCG Card Game Legendary Collection Set #5 LC5 5D's Box Set - 48 Cards (5 mega Packs boosters + 3 Promo Cards)
features: Takes Duelists through a futuristic and supercharged journey in Legendary Collection 5Ds, the latest entry in the popular Legendary Collection series.
